➜【星连文学社】苏坛：《雨住风轻的时候》
http://www.sohu.com/a/412459422_100115135	53767
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200810/b4641bd6da3e40fda77298a98a5d3a79.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《雨住风轻的时候》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雨住风轻的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">适合读一首诗或喝一杯咖啡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个人静静地想一想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书香的味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>金秋遇见爱情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>向日葵花也会发光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>谁在敲门</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>梦里走入我的心房</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落叶入耳，优美而静</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">请将阳光摇晃起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我想让岁月还自己一个梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200810/f00b19b4e5c7445aa5944064fc95a5c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
