➜【星连文学社】广西诗人陈熠明：云边梦幻玉荷生
http://www.sohu.com/a/412460277_100115135	54265
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200810/aa13378558954eed8736344267a923da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>云边梦幻玉荷生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•荷姑有梦自然香</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清波碧柳玉兰芳，沐浴烟霞静水藏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落影瑶池风正好，荷姑有梦自然香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•醉眼芙蓉梦雨亭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红笛岸上韵流听，醉眼芙蓉梦雨亭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧柳烟波芳影魅，摇风水面恋荷英。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（三）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•粉面衣裳梦水烟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水岸花明碧柳先，相逢只为聚前缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缠绵雨后娴淑影，粉面衣裳梦水烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200810/e25c5afcdfab44ffb4ee56ed0a51fbaf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（四）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•热恋荷花风有意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相邀水岸话重游，碧柳青蝉唱远幽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热恋荷花风有意，情缘雨夏又从头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（五）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•荷来清风醉远悠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日水云边落影愁，荷来清风醉远悠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">捷足始问芳心语，早有蜻蜓立上头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（六）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•洁心不染问清高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洁心不染问清高，梦里烟波碧柳摇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玉影瑶台风月下，回眸百媚笑天娇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200810/aa7949d7e7e446a78deb6e68bf1116b0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（七）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•荷缘水上遇今生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前尘有爱寄清风，并蒂花开梦里逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夏雨留虹飞彼岸，荷缘水上遇今生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（八）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•相约五里静亭轩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相约五里静亭轩，荡远兰舟夏雨前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">往事曾留沧海忆，花开只恋水云间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(九)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•荷心水面静潮流</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芳霞渐隐淡情愁，愿与清风梦远修。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">舍去凌云烟往事，荷心水面静潮流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200810/3a76a4b9411b4137926deeb1bbed9301.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﻿(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·花飞梦落水风前</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平湖仲夏留娇影，静美芳心话雨烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不染淤泥清远志，花飞梦落水风前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>﻿七绝·云边梦幻玉荷生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湖光醉色长风远，倩影瑶台月下逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑美芙蓉清水秀，云边梦幻玉荷生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·情荷水月梦如烟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相逢子夜瑶池上，并蒂花开正有缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玉影兰舟风柳岸，情荷水月梦如烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200810/38167a104ea9492d9a61510fe89b4ff9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200810/b02d64694e934584abf2c776fd4273e3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编：</strong> 丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200810/afbd78cf09464ea4b614abc1acf7c623.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
